{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he comes over to me, bends down by me, lit a light-- a lighter he had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had the opportunity to sneak in the water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I slipped in the water, bit a straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I swam under the water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the water turned like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The river was very fierce-- the River Styr, it goes through our hometown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a day or two, I somehow-- I was afraid to walk in daytime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They may pick me up again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I sneak through the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents were astonished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where were you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told them what had happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, people find out that I was one of the group that the Germans picked up on the riverbank.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they stood in line-- and, and waiting for me to tell them what happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I couldn't tell what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was one of the 3,000 victims.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which I said [? what I-- ?] hurt my heart to see when I was there in 1989.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to the same place, to, to see the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means-- the king of Poland, Lubartow, built a big castle in 1900 because it belonged to Poland, the town of Luck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this, this castle, they figured they're going to, to, to kill off the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw, to my astonishment, a man dressed up in, in a-- in a Ukrainian uniform, with a big mustache, the real [NON-ENGLISH], and chains on the hands, and chains on his feet.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the top was written down in Ukraine and Russian, which I know well, well, how to read because I studied Ukrainian and Russian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
